Shirley Grey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shirley_Grey 0 Shirley Grey (April 11, 1902 – August 12, 1981) was an American actress. She appeared in 46 films between 1930 and 1935. She was born in Naugatuck, Connecticut and died in Jacksonville Beach, Florida. Shirley_Grey ( April_11_,_1902 – August_12 , 1981 ) was an_American_actress .
